quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  112,1,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Yɛlima: “Ŋuna Naawuni nyɛla zaɣigaŋ.”"
  112,2,Naawuni nyɛla bɛ ni mali bukaata n-kpari So
  112,3,"O bi dɔɣi, bɛ mi bi dɔɣi O"
  112,4,O mi ka binshɛɣu din ŋmani O (binnamda puuni)
  113,1,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Yɛlima: “M-bɔri taɣibu ni asibaasi Duuma"
  113,2,Ka chɛ O ni nam shɛli zaɣibetali
  113,3,"Ni yuŋ zaɣibetali, di yi ti zibi"
  113,4,Ni paɣa shɛba ban tuhiri niŋdi kabiriti ni zaɣibetali
  113,5,"Ni nyubiɛɣu lana zaɣibetali, o yi ti zabi nyuli"
  114,1,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Yɛlima: “M-bɔri taɣibu ni ninsalinim’ Duuma"
  114,2,Ninsalinim’ Sulinsilana
  114,3,Ninsalinim’ Duuma jɛmdigu
  114,4,"Ka chɛ yɛltɔɣabiɛri lana (shintaŋ) zaɣibetali, ŋun sɔɣira"
  114,5,Ŋuna n-nyɛ ŋun zaŋdi yɛltɔɣa- biɛri m-birti ninsalinim’ suhiri ni
  114,6,Alizinnim’ mini ninsalinim’ puuni